{"tid":2147381,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子黃金泳灘瞭望塔上吊亡 胞弟黯然認屍　","createTime":"2020-08-09T08:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:52:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3073353b16fb280d50b33ada5501949ec564f28","tid":2147381,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200809/HSBUT3ILHJYHKP5QTNIXJBD5ZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200809%2FHSBUT3ILHJYHKP5QTNIXJBD5ZA%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminCIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=00311164\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200809%2FHSBUT3ILHJYHKP5QTNIXJBD5ZA%2F&h=75cb509d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200809/HSBUT3ILHJYHKP5QTNIXJBD5ZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n屯門黃金泳灘，早上8時許，晨運客發現一名年約40歲男子，在4號救生瞭望塔附近倒在泳灘上，昏迷不醒，通知救生員報警求助，救護員接報到場，證實男事主當場已氣絕身亡。毋須送院。警員在瞭望塔梯間發現一條斷了的尼龍繩，相信事主在梯間上吊，惟不勝負荷繩斷跌在泳灘上，泳灘附近發現啤酒罐，懷疑是死者留下。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後證實死者姓王（31歲），稍後警員聯絡了死者兩名胞弟到場，兩人黯然認屍及確認死者身份。據悉，事主受金錢及工作問題困擾，人員於現場沒有撿獲遺書，事件沒有可疑。"},{"pid":"f0774471de81d4f07e02be66bfdece914dac1d5d","tid":2147381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"是尻但啦 單單都冇可疑"},{"pid":"a68ee45911f441cbed63d3526aa90893314dccc2","tid":2147381,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d91a5feb5237e00d6d5ae9dd6c6ace1448684c","tid":2147381,"uid":309989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:25:07.000Z","msg":"上帝要入林鄭數, 唔係林鄭, 香港人洗咁慘?!"},{"pid":"78d2b2990f3fb8855e644eb9c4a64a7d94f7cadc","tid":2147381,"uid":138834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=